snippet.textDisplay:
YAMAN HU WALLAH HU LAZI LAILAAHAH ILLAHUWA
AR RAHMAAN ,AR RAHEEM, AL MALIKUL QUDDUS SALAMUL MUMINUL MUHAYMINUL AZEEZUL JABBAR
AL MUTAKABBIRUL KHAALIQUL BAARIUL MUSAWIRUL GHAFFAR ALQAHHARUL WAHHAABUL RAZZAQKUL FAATTAAHUL ALEEM
AL QAABIDUL BAASITUL KHAAFIDH AL RAAFIUL MUIZZUL MUZILUL SAMEEUL BASEERUL HAKAMUL 'ADL
AL LATEEFUL KHABEER ALHALEEMUL AZEEM AL GHAFOORUL SHAKOOR AL ALEEUL KABEERUL HAFEEDUL MUQEET
AL HASEEBUL JALEEL AL KAREEMUL RAQEEBUL MUJEEBUL WAASIUL HAKEEMUL WADOODUL MAJEEDUL BA'ITHUL SHAHEED
AL HAQQUL WAKEEL AL QAWIYYUL MATEEN AL WALIYYUL HAMEED AL MUHSEE MUBDIUL MU'ID AL MUHYEE MUMEETUL HAYYUL QAYYOOM
AL WAAJIDUL MAAJIDUL  WAAHIDUL *(AL AHAD)* SAMADUL QADIRUL MUQTADIRUL MUQADDIMUL MU'AKHIRUL AWWAL AAKHIR 
AL DAAHIRUL AL BAATINUL WAALI MUTA'ALI BARRUL TAWWABUL MUNTAQIMUL AFUWWUL RA'OOFUL MAALIK-UL-MULK DHUL-JALAALI WAL-IKRAAM
AL MUQSIT AL JAAMIUL GHANIYYUL MUGHNIUL MANIUL DHARR
AL NAFI NURUL HAADI BADEEUL BAAQIUL WAARITHUL RASHEEDUL SABOOR
